-1.title: Three's a Crowd
-1.plot: High school buddies Ricky Mendoza and Chris Daigle do everything together, but when a girl comes between them, jealousy and rage lead to a horrific act of violence. It takes police nearly a decade to unravel this twisted tale of revenge and murder.

1.title: The Ultimate Betrayal
1.plot: Kamisha Richards and Kayla Henriques grow up together in a housing project in Brooklyn, New York. The two girls become like sisters but their lives start to take different paths as Kamisha focuses on getting in to law school while Kayla falls in with the wrong crowd. The girls' friendship sours as Kayla becomes increasingly jealous of Kamisha's success, and Kamisha tires of Kayla's lack of gratitude. When a very public Facebook feud erupts no one could predict the deadly outcome.

2.title: Mommy Dearest
2.plot: When Darlene Haynes announces her pregnancy, best friend and roommate Julie Corey couldn't be happier. When Julie becomes pregnant as well, Darlene is overjoyed ands looks forward to raising their children together. But it is only the calm before the storm and soon everything will unravel to reveal a series of shocking betrayals beyond anyone's belief.

3.title: Lion's Den
3.plot: Insecure Jennifer Helmedach is instantly drawn to Faye Bennett, the friendly and self-assured new girl in town. The two girls become best friends but as they enter high school, Jennifer tires of being in Faye's shadow and starts hanging out with the wrong crowd. Little does Faye know, her generosity and concern for Jennifer will lead them both into a deadly trap.

5.title: Shattered Bonds
5.plot: Butch Pratt and Ed Swiger meet during their first year of college and join a fraternity. When they realize the frat is struggling to pay the bills, they devise a plan to make money, but no one could predict how the scheme would spiral out of control.

7.title: Bullied to Death
7.plot: Outgoing Megan Meier and shy Sarah Drew meet while in the 4th grade. The girls are bullied relentlessly at school and come to rely on each other for support. It seems like the two will be best friends forever until Megan hatches a plan to join the in-crowd and leave her friend Sarah behind. Hurt and rejected, Sarah plans her revenge. What begins as a plot to get back at Megan quickly spirals out of control and has consequences that will alter both of their lives forever.

8.title: Cruel Intentions
8.plot: Jennifer Daugherty and Angela Marinucci are two outcasts, but when the girls meet, they immediately become best friends. When Angela introduces Jennifer to her boyfriend, he unexpectedly begins hitting on Jennifer and a bitter love triangle develops that leads to backstabbing, lies, and betrayal. An angry confrontation follows and in a desperate attempt to win her man, one of the girls launches an elaborate scheme of revenge, torment and unimaginable violence.

9.title: Bitter Betrayal
9.plot: Alex Cover and Dequan Carter are best friends who spend every free moment together. But when Alex's brother commits suicide, Alex heads down a dangerous path. The boys drift apart until an ultimate betrayal brings the friendship to a shocking end.

12.title: Inner Demons
12.plot: A preacher's son and a rebel become unlikely best friends, but an accidental overdose drives a wedge between the two men. Resentment builds until one man's inner demons come out, leading to a tragic outcome that no one could have predicted

1.title: Roommate's Revenge
1.plot: After 40 years of friendship, roommates John Sulzbach and David Laws believe they know everything there is to know about one another. While one friend goes above and beyond to prove his loyalty, the other keeps dark secrets and has deadly intentions.

2.title: Thick as Thieves
2.plot: A famous NBA player's son, Nickey Van Excel, bonds with his best friend, Bradley Eyo, over their love of basketball. But when Nickey falls on hard times, he turns to risky robbery sprees to survive. Bradley agrees to help, leading to a deadly game.

3.title: Dying for a Baby
3.plot: Expecting mothers Angelique Robledo and Kassandra Toruga meet through a mutual friend and bond over the trials of their pregnancies. However, one of them wants more than just friendship from the other, and will do whatever it takes to get it.

4.title: Sliced and Diced
4.plot: Las Vegas blackjack dealers, Brenda Stokes and Joyce Rhone find friendship in the high stakes world of sin city. But when a man comes between the two women, one turns on the other, risking everything in a vengeful plot of kidnapping and murder.

5.title: Holy Murder
5.plot: When sixteen-year-old Chloe Ottman meets social outcast Francisco Cruz they become fast friends. But soon, a surprising secret and misleading intentions take these teenagers down a twisted and dangerous road full of lies and deceit.

6.title: The Closeted Killer
6.plot: High school buddies Ricky Mendoza and Chris Daigle do everything together, but when a girl comes between them, jealousy and rage lead to a horrific act of violence. It takes police nearly a decade to unravel this twisted tale of revenge and murder.

7.title: Fame and Misfortune
7.plot: Rapper Remy Smith and Makeda Barnes-Joseph spark a friendship on the NYC social scene. Their friendship and trust in one another grows until a devilish turn of events brings out the worst in one friend while leaving the other fighting for her life.

8.title: Text, Lies & Murder
8.plot: Brandy Stevens-Rosine and Jade Olmstead meet online and quickly bond over their coming out struggles. But jealousy and lies spin their friendship out of control, and when one girl finds a new love, their rollercoaster relationship turns deadly.

10.title: Maid of Dishonor
10.plot: Jamie Dennis discovers a new best friend in her babysitter, Anne Camp. Then, one seemingly routine night, as Anne watches Jamie's children, a chain reaction is set off that leads these friends to unfathomable betrayal and horrific violence.

11.title: Gang of Misfits
11.plot: Jared Whaley befriends loner Matt Baker at a Las Vegas high school. Matt suggests they sell drugs and becomes addicted to power and controlling their illegal empire. Can Jared keep his friend from spiraling out of control...or will he die trying?

12.title: Fire and Desire
12.plot: When high school student Amber Hess befriends classmate Todd Hoke they develop a trusted bond like brother and sister. But when one finds love, the ties that bind these friends begin to unravel, leading them to cross very dangerous lines.

6.title: Playing with Fire
6.plot: Quiet Nikki Rasmussen and party girl Jennifer Harris quickly become best friends. When Nikki agrees to help Jennifer plan her 30th birthday party, things take a turn for the worse. Jennifer blames the poor turnout on Nikki and a public Facebook fight ensues. Their decade long friendship goes up in smoke when the online feud crosses into the real world with devastating results.

9.title: Deviant Mind
9.plot: Crystal Todd and Ken Register meet and instantly become best friends. They are so close, Ken is considered part of Crystal's family. One night Crystal goes to a party, but never comes home. The next morning her body is found brutally raped and murdered and everyone in the small town is rocked by the horrific death of someone so well loved. But even more shocking is the discovery of who is responsible and the deviant, twisted secrets they are hiding.

10.title: The Snitch
10.plot: Misti Mayo is more outspoken while Christine Smith tends to keep her feelings inside, yet the two teenagers hit it off and become inseparable. But they soon become bored with small town life and the two run away to the big city of Fort Worth, Texas for adventure. At 17, Misti becomes pregnant by an older man and Christine is right by her side to support her. But one fateful night, a crazy robbery scheme pits the friends against each other and leads to a shocking act of betrayal and revenge that no one could have ever predicted.

imdb.plot outline: The bond between two friends seems unbreakable until lies, backstabbing, and betrayal turn a friendship into a gruesome nightmare. Friends who are at one time devoted to each other have things go horribly, and then fatally, wrong. Revenge plots turn fatal, bitter love triangles break hearts and very public online feuds erupt, resulting in deadly outcomes no one could predict.#ShockingButTrue
